<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>{{ title }} | おうちウェルネス</title>
  <meta name="description" content="{{ description or 'おうちヨガ・ウェルネスで毎日を整える。40〜50代女性のためのリアルな体験ブログ。' }}">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@300;400;700&family=Noto+Serif+JP:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --mauve:      #4B3B47;
      --dim-grey:   #6A6262;
      --grey-olive: #9C9990;
      --sand:       #CFD2B2;
      --blush:      #E0D8DE;
      --blush-light:#f5f1f3;
      --white:      #fff;
      --border:     #e8e2e5;
      --radius:     6px;
      --shadow:     0 2px 14px rgba(75,59,71,0.08);
      --shadow-h:   0 6px 24px rgba(75,59,71,0.14);
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
      color: var(--mauve);
      line-height: 1.85;
      background: var(--white);
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 300;
    }
    a { color: var(--mauve); text-decoration: none; }
    a:hover { color: var(--dim-grey); }
    img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }

    /* ===== ヘッダー ===== */
    .site-header {
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: var(--white);
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 100;
    }
    .header-inner {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 1.5rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      height: 60px;
    }
    .site-logo {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      color: var(--mauve);
    }
    .site-logo span { color: var(--grey-olive); }

    .header-nav ul {
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
    }
    .header-nav li a {
      display: block;
      padding: 0 1rem;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: var(--dim-grey);
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      line-height: 60px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
      transition: color 0.15s, border-color 0.15s;
    }
    .header-nav li a:hover {
      color: var(--mauve);
      border-bottom-color: var(--mauve);
    }
    .header-search {
      background: none; border: none;
      cursor: pointer; font-size: 1rem;
      color: var(--grey-olive); padding: 0.3rem;
    }

    /* ===== メインレイアウト（コンテンツ＋サイドバー） ===== */
    .site-body {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 2.5rem auto;
      padding: 0 1.5rem;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 280px;
      gap: 3rem;
      align-items: start;
    }
    .main-content { min-width: 0; }
    .sidebar { min-width: 0; }

    /* ===== サイドバー ===== */
    .sidebar-widget { margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
    .widget-title {
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      color: var(--mauve);
      padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
      border-bottom: 2px solid var(--mauve);
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    }

    /* プロフィール */
    .profile-avatar {
      width: 80px; height: 80px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      overflow: hidden;
      margin: 0 auto 0.8rem;
      border: 2px solid var(--blush);
    }
    .profile-avatar img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }
    .profile-name {
      text-align: center;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
      color: var(--mauve);
    }
    .profile-sub {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: var(--grey-olive);
      margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    }
    .profile-text { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--dim-grey); line-height: 1.8; }

    /* カテゴリ */
    .cat-list { list-style: none; }
    .cat-list li { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .cat-list li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .cat-list li a {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 0.55rem 0;
      font-size: 0.83rem;
      color: var(--dim-grey);
      transition: color 0.15s;
    }
    .cat-list li a:hover { color: var(--mauve); }
    .cat-count { font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--grey-olive); }

    /* タグ */
    .tag-cloud { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.45rem; }
    .tag-link {
      font-size: 0.73rem;
      padding: 0.18rem 0.65rem;
      border: 1px solid var(--blush);
      color: var(--dim-grey);
      transition: all 0.15s;
    }
    .tag-link:hover { background: var(--mauve); color: var(--white); border-color: var(--mauve); }

    /* 人気記事 */
    .popular-list { list-style: none; }
    .popular-item {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 24px 64px 1fr;
      gap: 0.6rem;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 0.75rem 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .popular-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .popular-num {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--sand);
    }
    .popular-thumb {
      width: 64px; height: 46px;
      object-fit: cover;
      border-radius: 3px;
    }
    .popular-title {
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
      color: var(--dim-grey);
    }
    .popular-title:hover { color: var(--mauve); }

    /* ===== フッター ===== */
    .site-footer {
      background: var(--mauve);
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
      text-align: center;
      padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
      margin-top: 4rem;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
    }
    .footer-logo {
      font-family: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--white);
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    }
    .footer-desc { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55); font-size: 0.82rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .footer-nav {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 1.5rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .footer-nav a { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); font-size: 0.78rem; }
    .footer-nav a:hover { color: var(--white); }
    .footer-copy { font-size: 0.73rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35); }

    /* ===== スマホ対応 ===== */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .site-body { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; padding: 0 1rem; margin: 1.5rem auto; }
      .sidebar { order: 2; }
      .main-content { order: 1; }
      .header-inner { padding: 0 1rem; }
      .header-nav { display: none; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header class="site-header">
    <div class="header-inner">
      <div class="site-logo">おうち<span>ウェルネス</span></div>
      <nav class="header-nav">
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/">ホーム</a></li>
          <li><a href="/">ヨガ体験談</a></li>
          <li><a href="/">ウェルネス習慣</a></li>
          <li><a href="/">初心者ガイド</a></li>
          <li><a href="/">プロフィール</a></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>
      <button class="header-search">🔍</button>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="site-body">
    <main class="main-content">
      {{ content | safe }}
    </main>

    <aside class="sidebar">

      <div class="sidebar-widget">
        <div class="widget-title">PROFILE</div>
        <div class="profile-avatar">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518611012118-696072aa579a?auto=format&fit=crop&w=180&h=180&q=80" alt="ひかる">
        </div>
        <div class="profile-name">ひかる</div>
        <div class="profile-sub">おうちウェルネス管理人</div>
        <p class="profile-text">おうちヨガを通じて、毎日を少しずつ整えています。40〜50代の方へ、正直な体験談をお届けします。</p>
      </div>

      <div class="sidebar-widget">
        <div class="widget-title">POPULAR</div>
        <ul class="popular-list">
          <li class="popular-item">
            <span class="popular-num">1</span>
            <img class="popular-thumb" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544367567-0f2fcb009e0b?auto=format&fit=crop&w=128&h=92&q=80" alt="">
            <a href="/posts/soelu-review/" class="popular-title">【体が硬い・体調不安な私でも】SOELUオンラインヨガを試した正直な体験談</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="sidebar-widget">
        <div class="widget-title">CATEGORY</div>
        <ul class="cat-list">
          <li><a href="/"><span>ヨガ体験談</span><span class="cat-count">1</span></a></li>
          <li><a href="/"><span>ウェルネス習慣</span><span class="cat-count">0</span></a></li>
          <li><a href="/"><span>初心者ガイド</span><span class="cat-count">0</span></a></li>
          <li><a href="/"><span>アイテム紹介</span><span class="cat-count">0</span></a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="sidebar-widget">
        <div class="widget-title">TAGS</div>
        <div class="tag-cloud">
          <a href="/" class="tag-link">SOELU</a>
          <a href="/" class="tag-link">オンラインヨガ</a>
          <a href="/" class="tag-link">初心者</a>
          <a href="/" class="tag-link">体が硬い</a>
          <a href="/" class="tag-link">40代</a>
          <a href="/" class="tag-link">リラックス</a>
          <a href="/" class="tag-link">おうち時間</a>
          <a href="/" class="tag-link">ウェルネス</a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </aside>
  </div>

  <footer class="site-footer">
    <div class="footer-logo">おうちウェルネス</div>
    <p class="footer-desc">体が硬くても、体調不安でも。おうちからはじめるウェルネスライフ</p>
    <nav class="footer-nav">
      <a href="/">ホーム</a>
      <a href="/">プロフィール</a>
      <a href="/">プライバシーポリシー</a>
      <a href="/">お問い合わせ</a>
    </nav>
    <p class="footer-copy">© 2026 おうちウェルネス</p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
